author: julianfoad
msg: Make the hash-based keywords-processing functions handle an empty hash
efficiently, and fix poor wording in one of their doc strings.  This is
Treat an empty hash in the same way as a null pointer, thus
avoiding the overhead of doing a no-op translation.
